Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.01,0:08:07.38,Italics,Tsugumi,0,0,0,,Som si istá, že sa Hitaki po čaji upokojí.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.93,0:08:09.79,Italics,Tsugumi,0,0,0,,Poviem mu všetko.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.26,0:08:12.67,Italics,Tsugumi,0,0,0,,Už nebudem nič tajiť.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.99,0:08:21.29,Default,Ouchi,0,0,0,,Vitaj doma, Tsugumi-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.29,0:08:22.77,Default,Female Servants,0,0,0,,Vitajte doma.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.08,0:08:24.54,Default,Tsugumi,0,0,0,,Som späť.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.54,0:08:27.00,Default,Tsugumi,0,0,0,,Dedko, priprav, prosím, čaj.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.00,0:08:27.77,Default,Ouchi,0,0,0,,Dobre.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.34,0:08:32.15,Default,Ouchi,0,0,0,,Pripravím Hitakiho obľúbený čaj Ceylon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.42,0:08:33.34,Default,Tsugumi,0,0,0,,Ďakujem.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.23,0:08:42.54,Default,Tsugumi,0,0,0,,Hitaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.81,0:08:45.77,Default,Tsugumi,0,0,0,,Počkaj!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.30,0:08:48.92,Default,Tsugumi,0,0,0,,Kúpila som ti novú knihu Migawa Shizuru-senseia!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.92,0:08:50.92,Default,Tsugumi,0,0,0,,A Éclair z Ugetsudo!
